<p>Alternatively, one can go to <tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">edge://flags/</span></tt> or <tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">chrome://flags/</span></tt> and change the <em>SameSite by default cookies</em> parameter to Disabled, which will allow users to log in with scpwiki.com domain.</p>
